OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1782317940
OL,3,CSchool's pioneering scheme to support
OL,4,Cboys with issues like the 'manosphere'
OL,6,FWhen Hampshire headteacher Chris
OL,7,FEdwards read a report called Lost Boys
OL,8,Fhe was shocked at the picture it
OL,9,Frevealed.
OL,11,FThe Centre for Social Justice
OL,12,Finvestigation detailed how boys are
OL,13,Fstruggling to keep up with the girls
OL,14,Fat every key stage of the education
OL,15,Fjourney, achieving on average half a
OL,16,Fgrade lower than girls in every GCSE
OL,17,Fsubject.
OL,19,FIt highlighted how men aged 16 to 24
OL,20,Fare more likely to be unemployed than
OL,21,Fwomen.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/16
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,387,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1782317940
OL,3,CSchool's pioneering scheme to support
OL,4,Cboys with issues like the 'manosphere'
OL,6,FAnd its statistics revealed how many
OL,7,Fyoung men are more likely to own a
OL,8,Fsmartphone than have a dad at home by
OL,9,Fthe time they leave secondary school
OL,10,Fat 16.
OL,12,FOn top of all that, he says he'd also
OL,13,Fpicked up a shift in the way some of
OL,14,Fhis male pupils were sometimes
OL,15,Fspeaking to the girls - and was
OL,16,Fworried about the impact of the so-
OL,17,Fcalled manosphere.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/16
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,387,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1782317940
OL,3,CSchool's pioneering scheme to support
OL,4,Cboys with issues like the 'manosphere'
OL,6,FHis response? To set up a unique
OL,7,Fmentoring scheme just for boys at his
OL,8,Fmixed secondary in Basingstoke called
OL,9,FBrighton Hill Community School.
OL,11,FNow, once a month dozens of boys aged
OL,12,F13 to 15 come together with men from
OL,13,Fthe local community who have
OL,14,Fvolunteered to act as positive role
OL,15,Fmodels.
OL,17,F"There is a crisis for young boys,"
OL,18,Fsaid Chris Edwards, "I don't know if
OL,19,Fit's a masculinity crisis, but they
OL,20,Fneed help.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/16
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,387,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1782317940
OL,3,CSchool's pioneering scheme to support
OL,4,Cboys with issues like the 'manosphere'
OL,6,F"A lot of the problems boys are facing
OL,7,Faren't of their own doing. They are
OL,8,Fbarriers that they're facing and they
OL,9,Fneed support and they need guidance.
OL,11,F"There are real hurdles and real
OL,12,Fchallenges they are battling against.
OL,13,FIssues that are caused by
OL,14,Ffatherlessness, they are veering into
OL,15,Fthis danger zone online.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/16
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,387,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1782317940
OL,3,CSchool's pioneering scheme to support
OL,4,Cboys with issues like the 'manosphere'
OL,6,F"And what I want to do, and what lots
OL,7,Fof people in education want to do, is
OL,8,Fget an arm around these boys and
OL,9,Freassure them that things are going to
OL,10,Fbe okay, and and see how we can start
OL,11,Fhelping to support them, to remove the
OL,12,Fbarriers in front of them."
OL,14,FMr Edwards and his team hold sessions
OL,15,Fwhere boys hear from aspirational
OL,16,Fkeynote speakers, work in small groups
OL,17,Fwith successful men from the worlds of
OL,18,Fsport, business and education, and are
OL,19,Fpaired with individual mentors.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/16
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,387,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1782317940
OL,3,CSchool's pioneering scheme to support
OL,4,Cboys with issues like the 'manosphere'
OL,6,FTheir objective - to get them to aim
OL,7,Fhigh, and try and counteract some of
OL,8,Fthe negative influences they might be
OL,9,Fsubjected to - whether that's crime,
OL,10,Fdrugs or online influences.
OL,12,FThe school is already starting to see
OL,13,Fa big difference in behaviour and
OL,14,Fattitudes since launching the GOAT
OL,15,Fboys project - which stands for
OL,16,FGreatest Of All The Boys.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/16
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,387,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1782317940
OL,3,CSchool's pioneering scheme to support
OL,4,Cboys with issues like the 'manosphere'
OL,6,FDeputy headteacher, Pete Beeching,
OL,7,Fsaid: "To be honest we started this
OL,8,Fnot knowing how the students would buy
OL,9,Finto it and their development and
OL,10,Ftheir growth has surpassed all of our
OL,11,Fexpectations."
OL,13,FChris Edwards told us: "What they are
OL,14,Fstarting to see from mixing with these
OL,15,Fvery successful men is that shortcuts
OL,16,Faren't the way forward and actually
OL,17,Freal success and real happiness comes
OL,18,Ffrom working hard and making something
OL,19,Fof yourself."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/16
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,387,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1782317940
OL,3,CSchool's pioneering scheme to support
OL,4,Cboys with issues like the 'manosphere'
OL,6,FAmong the volunteers is Al Fury, a
OL,7,Ffather of two who works for a computer
OL,8,Ffirm in Hampshire.
OL,10,F"What I want to demonstrate to them is
OL,11,Fsome of the values I had when I was
OL,12,Fgrowing up," said Al, "Things like
OL,13,Fbeing honest, getting up and going to
OL,14,Fwork.
OL,16,F"I worked hard, I wanted to earn money
OL,17,Fis a good way, but treat people with
OL,18,Frespect as well.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/16
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,387,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38609
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1782317940
OL,3,CSchool's pioneering scheme to support
OL,4,Cboys with issues like the 'manosphere'
OL,6,F"I think there's a lot of people out
OL,7,Fthere posting things which are sending
OL,8,Fthe wrong messages to young people."
OL,10,FFlinn, who is in Year 9, has already
OL,11,Flearned a lot from having Al as his
OL,12,Fmentor.
OL,14,F"It's very inspiring because he's very
OL,15,Fsuccessful in life," said Flinn. "You
OL,16,Flearn how to do things better.
OL,18,F"I think all young men should have the
OL,19,Fopportunity to do this because it's
OL,20,Fvery good and helpful."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G9/16
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,387,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38610
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1782317940
OL,3,CSchool's pioneering scheme to support
OL,4,Cboys with issues like the 'manosphere'
OL,6,FAnother of the mentors, Charlie
OL,7,FBaynes, runs his own highly successful
OL,8,Ftech company in Fareham. "I've run
OL,9,Fthis business for 27 years and we've
OL,10,Fgot over 100 staff so it's reasonably
OL,11,Fsuccessful.
OL,13,F"I want to help, I want to have an
OL,14,Fimpact. It's very easy to fall into
OL,15,Fthe wrong ways, the bad ways, and
OL,16,Fwe're here to help them."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G10/16
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
