OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,387,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38611
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1782317940
OL,3,CSchool's pioneering scheme to support
OL,4,Cboys with issues like the 'manosphere'
OL,6,FMany of the boys who are invited to
OL,7,Fjoin the scheme may have dads in their
OL,8,Flives, but have told the school in
OL,9,Fquestionnaires, that they feel they
OL,10,Flack a positive role model outside of
OL,11,Fthe home.
OL,13,FThey work on fundraising projects or
OL,14,Fsocial enterprise schemes with their
OL,15,Fmentors, learning skills and working
OL,16,Fas part of a team in monthly evening
OL,17,Fsessions.
OL,19,FThe plan now is to scale up the
OL,20,Fproject with at least 80 other schools
OL,21,Finterested in running similar schemes.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G11/16
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,387,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38612
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1782317940
OL,3,CSchool's pioneering scheme to support
OL,4,Cboys with issues like the 'manosphere'
OL,6,FWhen Bowen, who is also in Year 9, was
OL,7,Fasked what he thinks the mentors can
OL,8,Foffer he said: "Life skills and how to
OL,9,Fbe a man and stuff. "
OL,11,F"One day when I'm older I want to be
OL,12,Fthat awesome person."
OL,14,F"The first time I felt pretty
OL,15,Fembarrassed to come up here and all
OL,16,Fthat but it's getting more comfortable
OL,17,Fbeing here now and it's just becoming
OL,18,Fpart of my routine and I really enjoy
OL,19,Fcoming out here. "
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G12/16
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,387,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38613
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1782317940
OL,3,CSchool's pioneering scheme to support
OL,4,Cboys with issues like the 'manosphere'
OL,6,FSulaman, aged 14, said: "We've learnt
OL,7,Fhow to be motivated to stay on task,
OL,8,Fthat type of thing. Also I feel like
OL,9,Fit's keeping us a lot more
OL,10,Fresponsible. Before this I used to get
OL,11,Ftold off a lot more. I feel like I've
OL,12,Fbecoming a lot more mature through
OL,13,Fdoing this."
OL,15,FBy no means all of the boys taking
OL,16,Fpart are lacking a father figure at
OL,17,Fhome, but the school believes those
OL,18,Fselected are likely to benefit from
OL,19,Fextra guidance.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G13/16
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,387,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38614
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1782317940
OL,3,CSchool's pioneering scheme to support
OL,4,Cboys with issues like the 'manosphere'
OL,6,FThe free pizza encourages high
OL,7,Fattendance levels but it's not the
OL,8,Fmain reason the boys, or the men, are
OL,9,Fhere.
OL,11,FPeter Hanney said: "I'm a father of
OL,12,Ftwo boys myself and I think there's a
OL,13,Flot of negative influence out there on
OL,14,Fthe internet for young boys with the
OL,15,FAndrew Tates and people of this world
OL,16,Fbut there is also a lack of positive
OL,17,Finfluence talking to boys this age,
OL,18,Fshowing them their potential and what
OL,19,Fthey can do and what they can achieve.
OL,20,F"
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G14/16
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
