FL,387,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38615
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1782317940
OL,3,CSchool's pioneering scheme to support
OL,4,Cboys with issues like the 'manosphere'
OL,6,FJulia's 15 year old son has taken part
OL,7,Fin the programme and has benefited
OL,8,Fhugely.
OL,10,F"He was definitely going to, sort of,
OL,11,Fthe wrong direction. Since he started
OL,12,Fthe programme there's been a huge
OL,13,Fchange in him.
OL,15,F"The fact that there were people there
OL,16,Fthat were in the same position as him
OL,17,Fand have done really well for
OL,18,Fthemselves has been a big eye opener
OL,19,Ffor him. It's done wonders."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G15/16
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
